object.customQuery:
select distinct
sub.Claim_Key,
sub.LOSS_ACCOUNT_ENTERED_DATE,
sub.LOSS_TRANSACTION,
sub.LOSS_TRANSACTION_DATE,
sub.LOSS_CAUSE
from
(
select
master_losstrans.Claim_Key, 
master_losstrans.LOSS_ACCOUNT_ENTERED_DATE,
master_losstrans.LOSS_TRANSACTION,
master_losstrans.LOSS_TRANSACTION_DATE,
master_losstrans.Loss_Cause, 
row_number() over (partition by claim_key, loss_cause, loss_account_entered_date order by loss_transaction_date desc) as ClaimRank
from master_losstrans
where LOSS_TRANSACTION in ('22','23','41','42','43','66','92')
and claim_key is not null
) sub
join 
(SELECT distinct
master_losstrans.Claim_Key, 
master_losstrans.LOSS_ACCOUNT_ENTERED_DATE,
master_losstrans.LOSS_TRANSACTION,
master_losstrans.LOSS_TRANSACTION_DATE,
reopen.ReOpened_Dt as Reopen_Date,
master_losstrans.Loss_Cause
FROM master_losstrans
inner join
(select claim_key, 
LOSS_ACCOUNT_ENTERED_DATE, 
case when LOSS_TRANSACTION in ('66','92') then LOSS_TRANSACTION_DATE end as ReOpened_Dt, 
Loss_Cause
from master_losstrans
where case when LOSS_TRANSACTION in ('66','92') then LOSS_TRANSACTION_DATE end is not null) reopen
on master_losstrans.Claim_Key = reopen.Claim_Key
and master_losstrans.LOSS_ACCOUNT_ENTERED_DATE = reopen.LOSS_ACCOUNT_ENTERED_DATE
and master_losstrans.Loss_Cause = reopen.Loss_Cause
and reopen.ReOpened_Dt >= case when master_losstrans.LOSS_TRANSACTION in ('22','23','41','42','43' ) then master_losstrans.LOSS_TRANSACTION_DATE end) dupe
on sub.CLAIM_KEY = dupe.CLAIM_KEY
and sub.LOSS_ACCOUNT_ENTERED_DATE = dupe.LOSS_ACCOUNT_ENTERED_DATE
and sub.LOSS_CAUSE = dupe.LOSS_CAUSE
where ClaimRank = 1
order by Claim_Key

SELECT PMS_Fact_Loss.Loss_Cause_ID as Loss_Cause_ID, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Claim_Key as Claim_Key, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Loss_Cause as Loss_Cause, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Account_Entered_Dt as Account_Entered_Dt, 
max(PMS_Fact_Loss.Transaction_Dt) as Transaction_Dt 
FROM dbo.PMS_Fact_Loss
inner join dbo.constant_values cv on
cv.date_value=pms_fact_loss.account_entered_dt
where (PMS_Fact_Loss.Closed_Dt is not null or PMS_Fact_Loss.ReOpened_Dt is not null)
and PMS_Fact_Loss.Claim_Key is not null
and cv.name = 'current_period'
group by Claim_Key, loss_cause_id, Loss_Cause, Account_Entered_Dt
